 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Planificador de Viaje Cusco</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/Logo.png" />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#071329;
      --text:#e5eefc;
      --muted:#94a3b8;
      --green:#22c55e;
      --yellow:#facc15;
      --red:#ef4444;
      --blue:#38bdf8;
      --line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      --hero-overlay:rgba(7,19,41,.72);
      --card:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(23,32,51,.96),rgba(30,41,59,.96));
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background-color:var(--bg);
      position:relative;
      min-height:100vh;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }
    body::before{
      content:"";
      position:fixed; inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(var(--hero-overlay),var(--hero-overlay)),
        url('/hero.png') center top / cover no-repeat;
      z-index:-2;
      transform:translateZ(0);
    }
    body::after{
      content:"";
      position:fixed; inset:0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right,rgba(34,197,94,.10),transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top left,rgba(56,189,248,.10),transparent 24%);
      z-index:-1; pointer-events:none;
    }
    .container{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 18px 60px}
    .hero{
      position:relative;
      min-height:48vh;
      border-radius:28px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(9,18,36,.26),rgba(9,18,36,.52));
      margin-top:10px;
      margin-bottom:28px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      box-shadow:0 22px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)
    }
    .hero-inner{
      width:100%;
      padding:28px 30px 34px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:22px;
      align-items:center
    }
    .brand-lockup img{width:240px;height:auto;display:block}
    .hero-copy h1{font-size:42px;line-height:1.05;margin:12px 0 14px}
    .hero-copy p{color:#dbe7ff;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 18px}
    .hero-actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}
    .btn,.btn-secondary{
      border:none;border-radius:12px;padding:13px 18px;font-weight:800;
      cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center
    }
    .btn{background:var(--green);color:#04130a}
    .btn-secondary{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--line)}
    .hero-gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px}
    .hero-shot,.tour-card img,.day-photo{width:100%;display:block;object-fit:cover;border-radius:18px}
    .hero-shot{aspect-ratio:1.15 / 1;background:#172033}
    .section{margin-top:26px}
    .section h2{font-size:26px;margin:0 0 14px}
    .lead{color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 14px;line-height:1.6}
    .card{
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:18px;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.18)
    }
    .eyebrow{
      color:var(--muted);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
      margin-bottom:8px
    }
    .form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:12px}
    input,select{
      width:100%;
      background:#0f172a;color:var(--text);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:15px
    }
    .checkbox-grid{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:4px
    }
    .checkbox-item{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)
    }
    .checkbox-item input{width:auto;margin:0}
    .summary-bar{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
    .mini-card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:14px;padding:14px
    }
    .mini-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}
    .mini-value{font-size:22px;font-weight:800}
    .toolbar{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:14px}
    .toolbar-left,.toolbar-right{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
    .pill{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:999px;padding:8px 12px;
      font-weight:700;font-size:13px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid var(--line)
    }
    .pill.green{background:rgba(34,197,94,.14);color:var(--green)}
    .pill.orange{background:rgba(250,204,21,.12);color:var(--yellow)}
    .pill.red{background:rgba(239,68,68,.12);color:var(--red)}
    .pill.blue{background:rgba(56,189,248,.12);color:var(--blue)}
    .plan-days{display:grid;gap:14px}
    .day-card{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr;gap:16px;align-items:start}
    .day-photo{aspect-ratio:1.15 / .9;background:#172033}
    .day-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:12px}
    .day-title h3{margin:0 0 6px;font-size:22px}
    .day-title p{margin:0;color:var(--muted)}
    .day-body{display:grid;gap:12px}
    .line{color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.6}
    .warning,.info-note,.recommendation,.time-box{
      border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.55
    }
    .warning{background:rgba(250,204,21,.10);border:1px solid rgba(250,204,21,.18);color:#fde68a}
    .info-note{background:rgba(56,189,248,.10);border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.18);color:#bae6fd}
    .recommendation{background:rgba(34,197,94,.08);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.15);color:#dcfce7}
    .time-box{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--line);color:#e5eefc}
    .actions-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:10px}
    .selector-card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:14px
    }
    .selector-card h4{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:15px}
    .tour-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:14px}
    .tour-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden}
    .tour-card img{aspect-ratio:1.2 / .8;background:#172033}
    .tour-card .tour-copy{padding:14px}
    .tour-card h3{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px}
    .tour-card p{margin:0;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55}
    .hidden{display:none}
    @media (max-width:980px){
      .hero-inner,.day-card{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .summary-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}
    }
    @media (max-width:720px){
      .container{padding:16px 12px 40px}
      .hero-copy h1{font-size:34px}
      .hero-copy p{font-size:16px}
      .summary-bar{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .hero-gallery{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
      .mini-value{font-size:20px}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="brand-lockup"><img src="/Logo.png" alt="MachuLine" /></div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Planificador inteligente</div>
          <h1>Arma tu viaje ideal por Cusco, Machu Picchu y alrededores</h1>
          <p>Genera un itinerario día por día, ajusta actividades y transportes, y mira cómo cambian el tiempo, el costo y las recomendaciones en tiempo real.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#builder" class="btn">Crear mi plan</a>
            <a href="#tours" class="btn-secondary">Ver experiencias</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-gallery">
          <img class="hero-shot" src="/planificador/hero-machu.jpg" alt="Machu Picchu" />
          <img class="hero-shot" src="/planificador/hero-aguas.jpg" alt="Aguas Calientes" />
          <img class="hero-shot" src="/planificador/hero-cocalmayo.jpg" alt="Cocalmayo" />
          <img class="hero-shot" src="/planificador/hero-cusco.jpg" alt="Cusco" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="builder">
      <h2>Configura tu viaje</h2>
      <p class="lead">Primero definimos días, estilo y presupuesto base. Después armamos un itinerario real con horas de inicio, término, tiempo libre, comidas y recomendaciones.</p>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <div>
            <label for="days">Días en Cusco / zona</label>
            <select id="days">
              <option value="2">2 días</option>
              <option value="3" selected>3 días</option>
              <option value="4">4 días</option>
              <option value="5">5 días</option>
              <option value="6">6 días</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="style">Estilo de viaje</label>
            <select id="style">
              <option value="activo">Activo</option>
              <option value="relajado">Relajado</option>
              <option value="mixto" selected>Mixto</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="budget">Modo base</label>
            <select id="budget">
              <option value="economico">Económico</option>
              <option value="balanceado" selected>Balanceado</option>
              <option value="premium">Premium</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="arrival">Llegada a Cusco</label>
            <input type="datetime-local" id="arrival" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-top:16px;">Qué quieres incluir</div>
        <div class="checkbox-grid">
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="machu_picchu" checked /> Machu Picchu</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="valle_sagrado" checked /> Valle Sagrado</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="humantay" /> Laguna Humantay</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="vinicunca" /> Montaña 7 colores</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="palccoyo" /> Palccoyo</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="santa_teresa" /> Santa Teresa / Cocalmayo</label>
          <label class="checkbox-item"><input type="checkbox" value="cusco_city" checked /> Cusco ciudad</label>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <button class="btn" onclick="generarPlan()">Generar mi itinerario</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section hidden" id="result-section">
      <div class="toolbar">
        <div class="toolbar-left">
          <span class="pill blue" id="plan-badge">Plan generado</span>
          <span class="pill" id="effort-badge">Exigencia media</span>
        </div>
        <div class="toolbar-right">
          <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="undoPlan()">Atrás</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="redoPlan()">Adelante</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="summary-bar">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mini-label">Costo estimado</div>
          <div class="mini-value" id="summary-cost">US$0</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mini-label">Horas de traslado</div>
          <div class="mini-value" id="summary-transfer">0 h</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mini-label">Horas de actividades</div>
          <div class="mini-value" id="summary-activities">0 h</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mini-label">Tiempo libre</div>
          <div class="mini-value" id="summary-free">0 h</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mini-label">Comidas incluidas</div>
          <div class="mini-value" id="summary-meals">0</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="plan-output" class="plan-days"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="tours">
      <h2>Experiencias que puedes combinar</h2>
      <p class="lead">Puedes reemplazar estas imágenes por las definitivas. El objetivo es que la página se vea viva desde la primera versión.</p>

      <div class="tour-grid">
        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/machu.jpg" alt="Machu Picchu" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Machu Picchu</h3>
            <p>Separado de Aguas Calientes para planificar mejor noche previa, transporte y visita real.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/aguas.jpg" alt="Aguas Calientes" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Aguas Calientes</h3>
            <p>Nodo clave para descanso, termas, comida y acceso más limpio a Machu Picchu.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/valle.jpg" alt="Valle Sagrado" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Valle Sagrado</h3>
            <p>Muy útil para ordenar mejor el viaje antes de Ollantaytambo o Machu Picchu.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/humantay.jpg" alt="Laguna Humantay" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Laguna Humantay</h3>
            <p>Tour exigente, con opción de caminata o apoyo en caballo según el ritmo del viajero.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/vinicunca.jpg" alt="Montaña 7 colores" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Montaña 7 colores</h3>
            <p>Puede hacerse a pie, con caballo o con variantes más cómodas según disponibilidad.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tour-card">
          <img src="/planificador/cocalmayo.jpg" alt="Cocalmayo" />
          <div class="tour-copy">
            <h3>Santa Teresa + Cocalmayo</h3>
            <p>Diferencial real: termas, relax, canopy y posibilidad de noche alternativa en la zona.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

